{"tid":569721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你無眼花！！富榮花園居屋只係賣178萬咋！！","createTime":"2018-02-23T03:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T09:44:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e039c7cb9de35c5c67a7af9fb520f3cd7a3c5e55","tid":569721,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:16:22.000Z","msg":"富榮花園車位賣178萬　料貴絕全港居屋<br />\n02月22日(四) 19:20   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車位再錄高價買賣。旺角居屋富榮花園地下單號車位，以178萬元登記售出，料創居屋車位價新高，原業主2016年底以150萬元購入，帳面賺28萬元離場。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，自去年3月屋苑車位已曾錄約168萬元的高價成交，而本年初再錄另一宗達168萬元的車位買賣。家天下黎振傑稱，上述售出1期數個車位的月租，現時叫價多約4,200至4,500元，而現時買賣放盤約6至7個，叫價達180萬至200萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n如以月租叫價計算，是次售出車位租金回報率至少約2.8厘。但由於鄰近的私人屋苑帝柏海灣及柏景灣等的車位價格同時急升，加上放盤極為罕有，故部分業主亦意向轉購富榮花園車位自用。"},{"pid":"60ea16aae725f0cf7570662d234bcecb63309f3a","tid":569721,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/posts/10155797814487655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonccnews%2Fposts%2F10155797814487655&d=N%2B2JqFz4pVhGsMQ0kZHqCsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=b81bf430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/posts/10155797814487655</a>"},{"pid":"fa5f1721f9da1e1dcbb5a3cb0d9646d8cf7910cd","tid":569721,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50efb590fdb1e783ad7a6bdcf7a35e5dc2dd4b9","tid":569721,"uid":23052,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n富榮花園真係世界中心 <br />\n除左入大西北地區外 去邊都好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdb33028470519f1ace77d4a94a04589b66ee81","tid":569721,"uid":31920,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老味<br />\n富榮花園真係世界中心 <br />\n除左入大西北地區外 去邊都好方便<im